title: FSXP3D - FSPS Dolby Cockpit Sounds v1.8.0.0
description:
Real cockpit sounds for FSX software, produces real cockpit sounds that Flight Simulator engine can not do due to software limitations. All cockpit sounds production based to advanced mathematics and being calculated from the aircraft flight characteristics.
Many sounds can be heard from inside cockpit but FSPS focused to the ones that can add to your flight experience an extra 90% due to increase of your hear sensation. Due to this fact, you can improve your flight skills and your flight enjoy to an extra level.
The sounds that can do that are the wind sound from spoilers, flaps, gear, and brakes.
